      "body" : "The \"Loaded [...] banlist.dat\" is currently hidden in the net debug category: https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/d46b8b50fc3e725df75378db2d81aa48f9a1bd74/src/net.cpp#L1974",
